    "title": "How can you reduce the blockchain without losing coins in your wallet.",
    "body": "One approach to downscaling the blockchain.\r\n\r\n```\r\n\r\n    genesis block _____________________________________________________________________________\r\n         |                                                                                    |\r\n         |                                                                                    |\r\n    transaction block                                                                         |\r\n         |                                                                                    |\r\n         |                                                                                    |\r\n         |____________________________________________________________________                |\r\n            |                    |                     |                     |                |\r\n            |                    |                     |                     |                |\r\n        wallet 1              wallet 2              wallet 3              wallet 999...       | DELETE\r\n            |                    |                     |                     |                |\r\n            |                    |                     |                     |                |\r\n         |‾‾‾‾‾‾‾‾‾‾‾‾‾‾‾‾‾‾‾‾‾‾‾‾‾‾‾‾‾‾‾‾‾‾‾‾‾‾‾‾‾‾‾‾‾‾‾‾‾‾‾‾‾‾‾‾‾‾‾‾‾‾‾‾‾‾‾‾                |\r\n         |                                                                                    |\r\n         |                                                                                    |\r\n    transaction block                                                                         |\r\n         |                                                                                    |\r\n         |                                                                                    |\r\n         |                                                                                    |\r\n    wallet server 1 (genesis block) ‾‾‾‾‾‾‾‾‾‾‾‾‾‾‾‾‾‾‾‾‾‾‾‾‾‾‾‾‾‾‾‾‾‾‾‾‾‾‾‾‾‾‾‾‾‾‾‾‾‾‾‾‾‾‾‾‾‾‾\r\n         |\r\n         |\r\n         |\r\n    transaction block\r\n         |\r\n         |\r\n         |____________________________________________________________________\r\n            |                    |                     |                     |\r\n            |                    |                     |                     |\r\n        wallet 1              wallet 2              wallet 3              wallet 999...\r\n\r\n  \r\n```\r\n\r\nYou can do this once a year or once a month.\r\nblockchain size will drop to 10-20 mb after each cycle.\r\nWallets will not lose coins.",
